  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK442">
<l>uṟṟanōy nīkki yuṟāamai muṟkākkum </l>
<l>peṟṟiyārp pēṇik koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) procure and kindly care for men who can overcome difficulties when they occur, and guard against them before they happen.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
